Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is hard to define.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the reason is suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case's mystery is being solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will it be Conan, Heiji, or Jodie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Hattori suspected Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} of being with the Black Organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:02:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But while exiting the apartment building, we encountered a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the 21st floor, he fell to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the door was locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah like they claimed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, no one came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have been suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what we thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before we entered Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bedroom and saw this curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain has separated from the rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a few hooks are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This shows that he fell unsuspectingly and grabbed the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would someone committing suicide do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then, this wasn't suicide but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a case of murder, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,English Teacher vs. Western Detective, Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a locked room one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A locked room murder just like you see in the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I live next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two came to visit me, and just as we were exiting the building, Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, do you know the answer to this locked room murder mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm pretty sure the strange mark on that window has something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does look like something came in contact with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just finished developing Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most are just normal pictures of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we zoomed in on one and discovered something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew he was hanging by the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't he throwing something inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the mark on the glass is from the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did he throw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was angry with the caller?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,BE QUIET!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave this to the police! Civilians shouldn't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, if that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's got him so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, someone is always interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even so, they usually end up solving the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. How did the criminal make him fall out of the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was only taking pictures with her camera, so she could have used the flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there was nothing peculiar about Nakamichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we have Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think someone would jump because they were told to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I'm not sure about is why he tried to throw the phone back into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only possibility is that there is a clue on it and Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wanted us to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the cell phone didn't break when it fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there was nothing on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time... Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time is it? It's 8:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what time do you think it is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, I forgot I had to meet Kazuha today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You invited me to go to that restaurant Otaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} mentioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry... I can't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Heiji! Where are you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, a bad connection...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I don't think I can get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in Tokyo... Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll meet you as soon as I finish up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said we would meet in front of Umeda Bigman at 7-00!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:33.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Umeda Bigman is a large television screen at the Umeda Station located in the north center of Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I have in this memo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Memo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? An experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to do one now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we reenact what those three did before Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may finally understand this locked room murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was only taking pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} only sent a mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} only called Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means this wasn't a murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's check.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we Ye missing something important for this experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was drunk before he went to sleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but who is going to play the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just it, officers can't drink while on duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm underage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the only one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But can you get the alcohol I love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very, very delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,[s that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's very tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:10:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright Inspector, can you give us a second to get ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nakamichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you cal! us up here to the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why is that foreign woman lying on Takai-sans bed drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We re having an experiment to reenact what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get everything ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} is asleep on the bed and I've put my cell phone by her pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we made a little change without her knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you change?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, it's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's begin the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:11:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, Nakamichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sent a mail to Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s phone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, so I'll send a mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Sensei, did you get that mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, it's a lovely mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of mail was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next thing was Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} taking pictures of the building outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, will all of this really reveal the trick behind the locked room murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something we'll know when it's over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last step is Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's just talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK... what about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about that mail I sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about that mail I sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not a mere boy, are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not a mere boy, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. I'm just a normal high-school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to hear you, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! This is apartment is so high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This often happens when I use my phone up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go outside, you can hear me better from the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you. Officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, we moved the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} would go out onto the balcony to better the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei tried to get out onto the balcony from the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyone that had been drinking would go straight from the bed to the opposite window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like how Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} would have fallen like Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} if I hadn't told her about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right the one who talked to Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} up to his final moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawakami Noboru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before, he moved Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bed from its original position, beside of this window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the opposite window that lacks a balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left his bed and climbed out, falling to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably moved the bed while Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was drinking with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} likely claimed he was going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He snuck into Takai-sans room to move the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, as Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came in and passed out on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He placed his cell phone beside of his pillow to complete his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then all you would have to do is call and claim you couldn't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't he!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} had fallen during this experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because look...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We tied a rope to Sensei's waist without her knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is very clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should explain how you killed him to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah if I did anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that I moved the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he wanted me to change it around for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm still surprised, that this is why he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't even notice it until you mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Takai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can apologize to Hiraya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} from hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That you left a message like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't notice it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:17:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} held onto that curtain for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He pressed the memory button and recorded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The proof that you killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are the words you shared with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To avenge the death of your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are, your camera from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must thank you, for pretending you were tricked earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't got your name yet, have [?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be more interesting to talk about your true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:17:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you pretend you can't speak good English when you're actually great at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I asked you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You're not a mere boy, are you?" You said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Yes, I'm only a normal high school student."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said "yes", because "yeah" means "no" in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Yes" is how a foreigner would reply, but you replied with a proper English "yes" because I'm foreign.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably answered in such a proper way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you knew English is my first language.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am an English teacher, you can't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well actually, I wasn't pretending not to be able to speak English, but uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did silence work better than your funnily disguised Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Japanese is perfect, yet it has an odd intonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that you're disguising your Japanese to deter people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, hopefully we can talk about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he already knew that much, why did he set up this experiment and get her drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were right about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She took our pictures, and pretended about the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her hair and body were wet yet the hair dryer on the floor was warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body lotion hadn't dried yet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was probably taking a bath as we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But took a shower to buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, but I wonder why she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watching us during the entire case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I removed the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Sensei's suspicious, but she doesn't seem bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, her face was nothing like that American actress Chris Vineyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they both do have big breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's really her appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right shouldn't you be gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't she waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! I forgot about...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All about meeting Kazuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-A-Anyway, be careful Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're smart enough to steal from the police, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotta run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If any other strange people appear, let me know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can always call me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} isn't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are others...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori Heiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.71,0:23:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An interesting boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The son of the Osaka Police Chief, Hattori Heizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like Kudo Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Private Eye.
